## Keyboard Navigation

### Tab Order

- [ ] Tab order follows visual reading order (left-to-right, top-to-bottom)
- [ ] All interactive elements are reachable via Tab key
- [ ] Custom components implement proper `tabindex` (0 for focusable, -1 for programmatic focus)
- [ ] No `tabindex` values greater than 0

### Focus Management

- [ ] Focus indicator is visible on all interactive elements
- [ ] Custom focus styles have at least 3:1 contrast ratio
- [ ] Focus moves logically when modal dialogs open/close
- [ ] Focus returns to trigger element when closing dialogs
- [ ] Skip navigation link present as first focusable element

```css
/* Visible focus indicator */
:focus-visible {
  outline: 2px solid var(--color-focus);
  outline-offset: 2px;
}
```

### Keyboard Shortcuts

- [ ] Escape closes modals and popovers
- [ ] Enter activates buttons and links
- [ ] Space toggles checkboxes and buttons
- [ ] Arrow keys navigate within composite widgets (tabs, menus, listboxes)

